    {
      "type": "text", "id": "ci_title",
      "x": 1036, "y": 232, "width": 380, "height": 22,
      "text": "stage 1   cloud-init   (one-shot)",
      "originalText": "stage 1   cloud-init   (one-shot)",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e40af", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 300076, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 300077,
      "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "ci_body",
      "x": 1036, "y": 260, "width": 388, "height": 180,
      "text": "apt install:\n  python3.12, python3.12-venv\n  caddy, docker.io, git\n\nwrite secret files (from TF_VAR_*):\n  /opt/voicehook/.env          (0600)\n  /etc/voicehook/gcp-sa.json   (0600)\n  /etc/livekit/livekit.yaml    (0600)\n\ngit clone github.com/voicehook-ai/voicehook-v4\n  /opt/repo\n\nrun  BOX_HOST=local bash /opt/repo/deploy/deploy.sh",
      "originalText": "apt install:\n  python3.12, python3.12-venv\n  caddy, docker.io, git\n\nwrite secret files (from TF_VAR_*):\n  /opt/voicehook/.env          (0600)\n  /etc/voicehook/gcp-sa.json   (0600)\n  /etc/livekit/livekit.yaml    (0600)\n\ngit clone github.com/voicehook-ai/voicehook-v4\n  /opt/repo\n\nrun  BOX_HOST=local bash /opt/repo/deploy/deploy.sh",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 300078, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 300079,
      "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle", "id": "deploy_section",
      "x": 1020, "y": 470, "width": 420, "height": 420,
      "strokeColor": "#6d28d9", "backgroundColor": "#ede9fe",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 300080, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 300081,
      "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "deploy_title",
      "x": 1036, "y": 482, "width": 380, "height": 22,
      "text": "stage 2   deploy.sh   (idempotent, re-runnable)",
      "originalText": "stage 2   deploy.sh   (idempotent, re-runnable)",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#5b21b6", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 300082, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 300083,
      "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "id": "deploy_body",
      "x": 1036, "y": 510, "width": 388, "height": 370,
      "text": "1. rsync code  ->  /opt/voicehook  (exclude .git, tests)\n\n2. python3.12 -m venv /opt/voicehook/.venv\n   .venv/bin/pip install -e .\n\n3. install systemd unit\n   /etc/systemd/system/voicehook-agent.service\n   systemctl daemon-reload\n   systemctl enable --now voicehook-agent\n\n4. render Caddyfile from\n     infra/caddy/Caddyfile.tmpl\n   substituting  var.caddy_site_main\n                 var.caddy_site_rtc\n   caddy validate  ->  systemctl reload caddy\n\n5. docker pull livekit/livekit-server\n   docker rm -f livekit  (if exists)\n   docker run -d --name livekit --net=host \\\n     -v /etc/livekit:/etc/livekit \\\n     livekit/livekit-server --config /etc/livekit/livekit.yaml\n\n6. smoke check:\n   curl http://127.0.0.1:7400/api/healthz",
      "originalText": "1. rsync code  ->  /opt/voicehook  (exclude .git, tests)\n\n2. python3.12 -m venv /opt/voicehook/.venv\n   .venv/bin/pip install -e .\n\n3. install systemd unit\n   /etc/systemd/system/voicehook-agent.service\n   systemctl daemon-reload\n   systemctl enable --now voicehook-agent\n\n4. render Caddyfile from\n     infra/caddy/Caddyfile.tmpl\n   substituting  var.caddy_site_main\n                 var.caddy_site_rtc\n   caddy validate  ->  systemctl reload caddy\n\n5. docker pull livekit/livekit-server\n   docker rm -f livekit  (if exists)\n   docker run -d --name livekit --net=host \\\n     -v /etc/livekit:/etc/livekit \\\n     livekit/livekit-server --config /etc/livekit/livekit.yaml\n\n6. smoke check:\n   curl http://127.0.0.1:7400/api/healthz",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
